      • makeBackupName

        public static java.lang.String makeBackupName​(java.lang.String standardName,
                                              long highZxid)
        Creates a file name string for a backup file by appending a high zxid/long in Hex if it doesn't already contain an ending zxid. It also adds the snapshot filename StreamMode extension in case snapshot compression is enabled. E.g.) snapshot.123.snappy -> snapshot.123-456.snappy
        Parameters:
        standardName -
        highZxid -
        Returns:
